stuck visiting my grandmother.

30
00:03:43,541 --> 00:03:47,083
Well, at least she lives
by the Seto Inland Sea.

31
00:03:52,791 --> 00:03:54,666
[NAGASUMI]
Whoa, what?

32
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:57,208
You're kidding me, there's
only one bus every hour?

33
