[GRANDMOTHER] You betcha!
That made your grandpa happy.

54
00:04:56,250 --> 00:04:58,291
[NAGASUMI]
Oh... cool.

55
00:04:59,666 --> 00:05:01,083
[GRANDMOTHER] I'm so
sorry ya had to make

56
