first day of his vacation.

68
00:05:28,083 --> 00:05:30,000
I know, I know.

69
00:05:30,083 --> 00:05:32,458
Can we just forget about
school while we're here?

70
00:05:32,541 --> 00:05:34,000
Thanks to his grades,
he spent the

71
