[MOM] He's not the
world's greatest student.

75
00:05:42,250 --> 00:05:43,666
[grandmother laughs]

76
00:05:43,750 --> 00:05:45,750
[GRANDMOTHER] That's nothin'.
I hardly doubt ya could be

