97
00:06:28,333 --> 00:06:30,083
[NAGASUMI] You gonna
sleep in your bathing suit?

98
00:06:30,166 --> 00:06:31,250
I can't believe how

99
00:06:31,333 --> 00:06:33,333
hyperactive you've
been acting dad.

100
00:06:33,416 --> 00:06:34,583
[DAD] Well, you're
not hyper enough!

101
00:06:34,666 --> 00:06:36,000
Why don't you act like a kid?

102
00:06:36,083 --> 00:06:38,291
Summer vacation will
be over before you know it!

103
00:06:38,375 --> 00:06:40,666
You should be running wild
with snot-nosed joy and

104
