Help, I'm drowning!

116
00:07:06,208 --> 00:07:07,416
[NAGASUMI] It hurts so much.

117
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:09,625
No. I don't
wanna die.

118
00:07:14,333 --> 00:07:16,541
[NAGASUMI] Mom.
Dad. Somebody.

119
00:07:16,625 --> 00:07:18,833
Please.
Anybody.

120
00:07:20,625 --> 00:07:23,875
Someone help me.

121
00:07:30,791 --> 00:07:31,833
[DAD]
Nagasumi.

122
00:07:31,916 --> 00:07:34,125
Hey!
Nagasumi!

123
00:07:36,333 --> 00:07:37,750
[NAGASUMI] What the--?

124
00:07:37,833 --> 00:07:40,250
Do you have any idea how long
I've been looking for you?

125
00:07:40,333 --> 00:07:42,666
What the heck are you
sleeping down here for?

126
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:45,208
I was starting to think
that you'd drowned!

127
00:07:45,291 --> 00:07:46,500
[NAGASUMI] Dad?

128
00:07:46,583 --> 00:07:48,166
[DAD] Were you
expecting someone else?

129
00:07:48,250 --> 00:07:49,416
Jeez.

130
00:07:49,500 --> 00:07:51,875
[DAD] Come on, let's
head back to Grandma's.

131
