Dad, wait!

132
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:57,041
But I did drown!
I mean, I was drowning.

133
00:07:57,125 --> 00:07:59,416
And well, see,
I was really far offshore.

134
00:07:59,500 --> 00:08:01,625
[DAD] Are you serious?
You were drowning and the

135
00:08:01,708 --> 00:08:04,083
