247
00:12:16,541 --> 00:12:17,458
[NAGASUMI] M-Mermaid!

248
00:12:17,541 --> 00:12:19,708
She's the one from
this afternoon!

249
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:25,541
[GOZABURO] Hey, kid.
Wake up.

250
00:12:26,791 --> 00:12:28,750
