255
00:12:37,333 --> 00:12:39,083
[NAGASUMI] I'm fine!
Get up! Get off!

256
00:12:39,166 --> 00:12:41,500
[MOM] I know I shouldn't
be jealous of my son, but...

257
00:12:41,583 --> 00:12:43,916
You do know I can
hear you, dontcha?

258
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,166
Don't just sit there!
Why didn't you stop him?

259
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:48,333
