say it out loud.

262
00:12:51,583 --> 00:12:55,041
[GOZABURO] Somethin' wrong, kid?
Ya seem pretty agitated.

263
00:13:00,500 --> 00:13:02,666
So, uh, where
are we exactly?

264
00:13:02,750 --> 00:13:06,041
Well, Nagasumi, we're in Sun's
house, at the bottom of the sea.

265
00:13:06,125 --> 00:13:07,583
It's a house for mermaids.

266
00:13:07,666 --> 00:13:10,083
[GOZABURO] Thanks for makin'
the trip all the way down here.

267
00:13:10,166 --> 00:13:12,458
I'm Sun's father,
but most people know me

268
00:13:12,541 --> 00:13:15,750
as the boss of the local outfit
of the Seto Fish Commision.

269
00:13:15,833 --> 00:13:18,375
[GOZABURO] My name
is Gozaburo Seto.

270
00:13:20,416 --> 00:13:21,666
I'm Ren Seto.

271
00:13:21,750 --> 00:13:23,666
His lovely wife
and Sun's mother.

272
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:24,500
[NAGASUMI THINKS]
We're being held captive

273
00:13:24,583 --> 00:13:26,416
by genuine mobsters!

274
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:27,916
How could
you do this to us?

275
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,666
After all we've
done for you.

276
00:13:30,125 --> 00:13:31,791
Alright, enough
of the small talk,

277
00:13:31,875 --> 00:13:33,750
let's just cut
to the chase here.

278
00:13:33,833 --> 00:13:35,875
I brought you all down here 'cuz

279
00:13:35,958 --> 00:13:38,666
my daughter saved your
son's life today.

280
00:13:38,750 --> 00:13:40,041
She saved your life?

281
00:13:40,125 --> 00:13:41,333
Why didn't you
tell us that?

282
00:13:41,416 --> 00:13:42,541
I did!

283
00:13:42,625 --> 00:13:44,958
I told you a mermaid
saved me from drowning!

284
00:13:45,041 --> 00:13:47,458
[GOZABURO] Now listen close
to what I'm about to tell ya.

285
00:13:47,541 --> 00:13:49,625
We live by the code
of the Mermaid law

286
00:13:49,708 --> 00:13:51,708
and according to it,
any mermaid that

287
00:13:51,791 --> 00:13:54,041
lets a human see
their true form...

288
00:13:54,666 --> 00:13:57,625
...is sentenced
to death by execution!

289
00:13:58,166 --> 00:14:01,000
[GOZABURO] We send em' off
to sleep with the fishes, see?

290
00:14:01,083 --> 00:14:03,041
And there ain't nothing
we can do about it!

291
00:14:03,125 --> 00:14:04,541
It has to be done!

292
00:14:04,625 --> 00:14:05,791
Ain't that a pity?

293
00:14:05,875 --> 00:14:07,958
Ain't that a pity my
daughter has to die?

294
00:14:08,041 --> 00:14:08,708
[DAD] Uh-huh.

295
00:14:08,791 --> 00:14:09,625
[NAGASUMI] Uh.
Yeah.

296
00:14:09,708 --> 00:14:10,708
[MOM] Certainly.

297
00:14:10,791 --> 00:14:12,791
And it's all yer
fault, ya little shit!

298
00:14:12,875 --> 00:14:14,375
Why the hell should
my daughter have to

299
00:14:14,458 --> 00:14:16,625
die just cuz' you don't
know how to swim? Huh?

300
00:14:16,708 --> 00:14:18,583
[NAGASUMI] I don't know
how to answer that!

301
00:14:18,666 --> 00:14:19,833
[REN] Now dear.

302
00:14:20,250 --> 00:14:22,583
So this whole snafu
got me ta' thinkin'.

303
00:14:22,666 --> 00:14:25,916
Why should a mermaid have
ta die just fer bein' seen.

304
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,208
[GOZABURO] When I
can solve the problem

305
00:14:27,291 --> 00:14:29,333
by killing the human
who saw her instead?

306
00:14:29,416 --> 00:14:30,708
--That's it!
--Don't sacrifice me!

307
00:14:30,791 --> 00:14:32,166
--I'll just have you killed.
--Don't sacrifice me!

308
00:14:32,250 --> 00:14:33,375
--Hell I'll kill you myself
--Boss, please calm down!

309
00:14:33,458 --> 00:14:34,375
--right now you little BASTARD!
--Calm down!

310
00:14:34,458 --> 00:14:35,708
You've got nothing
to worry about.

311
00:14:35,791 --> 00:14:37,708
You just leave things to me.

312
00:14:37,791 --> 00:14:39,166
[BOTH] 'kay.

313
00:14:39,250 --> 00:14:40,708
--I'm gonna harpoon that 
--This is no time for weird

314
00:14:40,791 --> 00:14:43,083
--little piece of fecal matter.
--mother and son fantasies!

315
00:14:43,166 --> 00:14:44,541
[GOZABURO] Let me go!

316
00:14:44,625 --> 00:14:46,958
--[SUN] Knock it off, Dad!
--Let me go! He has to die!

317
00:14:47,041 --> 00:14:48,125
Ya can't kill him!

318
00:14:48,208 --> 00:14:50,833
I saved him so that
he wouldn't die!

319
00:14:50,916 --> 00:14:52,583
[SUN] And killin' him for
no reason is just as

320
00:14:52,666 --> 00:14:54,958
