according to the mob code. 

321
00:14:55,041 --> 00:14:56,208
But Sun....

322
00:14:56,291 --> 00:14:58,625
...the code says ya have
to die fer savin' him.

323
00:14:58,708 --> 00:15:00,250
Yeah, and I
can accept that!

324
00:15:00,333 --> 00:15:03,666
I meant ta save his life.
It's my choice.

325
00:15:04,916 --> 00:15:05,958
Go on...

326
00:15:06,041 --> 00:15:08,041
Go ahead: boil me,
grill me, whatever!

327
00:15:08,125 --> 00:15:09,750
[GOZABURO] How
can ya say that, Sun?

328
00:15:09,833 --> 00:15:11,208
Please, just let
Daddy waste this

329
00:15:11,291 --> 00:15:13,791
worthless human and
everything will be fine!

330
00:15:13,875 --> 00:15:16,333
[DAD] Thanks for ruining
our vacation, Nagasumi.

331
00:15:16,416 --> 00:15:18,083
[NAGASUMI] Shouldn't
you be trying to save me,

332
00:15:18,166 --> 00:15:20,500
instead of blaming me?

333
00:15:20,583 --> 00:15:23,041
I really do apologize.
Once my husband's blood

334
00:15:23,125 --> 00:15:25,666
starts to boil,
there's no stopping him.

335
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:26,916
Uh, that's okay.

336
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:29,083
And my daughter is
typically very respectful,

337
00:15:29,166 --> 00:15:31,375
but she's got this
stubborn streak about her.

338
00:15:31,458 --> 00:15:32,500
Is that so?

339
00:15:32,583 --> 00:15:34,791
It certainly is, Nagasumi.

340
00:15:34,875 --> 00:15:36,791
We have to adhere
to the mermaid code,

341
00:15:36,875 --> 00:15:38,208
but there is one
solution that doesn't

342
00:15:38,291 --> 00:15:40,875
involve any of this
killing nonsense.

343
00:15:41,416 --> 00:15:43,375
[GOZABURO] No!
Don't tell 'em!

344
00:15:43,458 --> 00:15:45,750
Well you see, Nagasumi.

345
00:15:45,833 --> 00:15:49,666
All you have to do
is marry our daughter.

346
00:15:53,750 --> 00:15:55,166
