347
00:15:55,250 --> 00:15:58,041
[REN] Once you're family,
you can know Sun's true form.

348
00:15:58,125 --> 00:16:00,000
It wouldn't be an issue then.

349
00:16:00,083 --> 00:16:02,791
So, what do ya say?
You'll marry into the family,

350
00:16:02,875 --> 00:16:04,041
won't ya handsome?

351
00:16:04,125 --> 00:16:05,125
[Gozaburo growls]

352
00:16:05,208 --> 00:16:07,666
[GOZABURO] Well,
Mr. and Mrs. Michishio.

353
00:16:07,750 --> 00:16:10,083
[GOZABURO] I hate to
say so, but there ya have it.

354
00:16:10,166 --> 00:16:11,666
[GOZABURO]
Yer unworthy son can marry

355
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:14,250
my precious, wonderful,
beautiful daughter.

356
00:16:14,333 --> 00:16:17,000
He'll take her as his bride,
or we'll just have to

357
00:16:17,083 --> 00:16:19,875
murder every human
that knows about us.

358
00:16:21,166 --> 00:16:24,375
[GOZABURO] And that includes
the two of you as well.

359
00:16:24,458 --> 00:16:27,291
As I'm sure you've
figured out by now.

360
00:16:27,375 --> 00:16:30,958
Murder every human.
That includes the two of you.

361
00:16:31,041 --> 00:16:33,375
You're really gonna love
being married, Nagasumi.

362
00:16:33,458 --> 00:16:35,958
[MOM] I'm just overcome
with joy for you.

363
00:16:36,041 --> 00:16:37,333
[NAGASUMI] Look me
in the eye and say that.

364
00:16:37,416 --> 00:16:38,666
That's right.
Your parents are always

365
00:16:38,750 --> 00:16:40,875
looking out for you,
and we couldn't be happier.

366
00:16:40,958 --> 00:16:43,208
[NAGASUMI]Why don't you use
your left hook on him, Dad?

367
00:16:43,291 --> 00:16:45,833
[MOM] He's all worn out
from using it on you earlier.

368
00:16:45,916 --> 00:16:47,375
[GOZABURO] Somethin'
wrong with ya, punk?

369
00:16:47,458 --> 00:16:49,291
Ya tellin' me that ya
don't think my daughter's 

370
00:16:49,375 --> 00:16:50,666
good enough for
you or somethin'?

371
00:16:50,750 --> 00:16:52,000
