372
00:16:52,083 --> 00:16:53,500
I just don't think you
should rush us like this!

373
00:16:53,583 --> 00:16:55,125
I mean, you can't force love.

374
00:16:55,208 --> 00:16:57,083
We don't even
know each other yet.

375
00:16:57,166 --> 00:16:59,291
There's a good chance
that she won't even...

376
00:16:59,375 --> 00:17:02,875
Um, wanna marry me.

377
00:17:03,458 --> 00:17:04,625
[GOZABURO]
Shut yer face, maggot!

378
00:17:04,708 --> 00:17:06,250
My daughter's ready
to die and yer givin'

379
00:17:06,333 --> 00:17:08,000
me this 'get to
know each other' crap?

380
00:17:08,083 --> 00:17:09,333
[GOZABURO] There's no
way in hell I'll let

381
00:17:09,416 --> 00:17:11,250
her marry a pathetic
piss ant like you!

382
00:17:11,333 --> 00:17:14,208
I'll kill you!
You small weak fleshy--

383
00:17:14,291 --> 00:17:15,708
[REN]  Now, dear!

384
00:17:15,791 --> 00:17:17,666
Ya oughta respect the bravest
decision of a girl's life!

385
00:17:17,750 --> 00:17:20,166
Masa! Don't you
let him get away!

386
00:17:22,083 --> 00:17:23,958
[NAGASUMI] Wait!
How can you do this!

387
00:17:24,333 --> 00:17:26,291
[NAGASUMI THINKS]
You gave me my first kiss.

388
00:17:26,375 --> 00:17:27,791
Well, Nagasumi...

389
00:17:27,875 --> 00:17:30,583
Sorry it turned out like this,
but I don't have a choice.

390
00:17:30,666 --> 00:17:32,750
You'd be dead if it
weren't for her, so it only

391
00:17:32,833 --> 00:17:35,166
makes sense that you
give your life for her now.

392
00:17:35,250 --> 00:17:37,375
[NAGASUMI] That doesn't
make sense at all!

393
00:17:37,458 --> 00:17:39,166
[GANGSTER C]
Hold it right there!

394
00:17:39,250 --> 00:17:40,583
[GANGSTER D] Yahoo!
It's exterminatin' time!

395
00:17:41,875 --> 00:17:44,791
[NAGASUMI] What the hell?
Why won't this door open?

396
00:17:45,625 --> 00:17:48,250
[NAGASUMI] Come on!
Open dammit!

397
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:54,708
