398
00:17:54,791 --> 00:17:56,958
[GANGSTER E] The water
swept him into the house.

399
00:17:57,041 --> 00:17:59,166
[GOZABURO] Rip him
to shreds, Shark Fujishiro!

400
00:17:59,250 --> 00:18:00,625
Shark Fujishiro?

401
00:18:00,708 --> 00:18:02,416
[SHARK]
