402
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:04,291
[NAGASUMI] Holy crap,
he's a literal shark!

403
00:18:05,166 --> 00:18:07,458
[SUN] Sorry Fujishiro,
ya can't eat him.

404
00:18:07,541 --> 00:18:09,291
[SHARK]
Why'd ya take my food?

405
00:18:09,375 --> 00:18:12,083
Uh, wow, thank you.
You saved me again.

406
00:18:12,166 --> 00:18:13,416
Sun right?

407
00:18:13,791 --> 00:18:14,875
Hurry!

408
00:18:14,958 --> 00:18:16,625
We'll sneak out through
the back entrance!

409
00:18:22,208 --> 00:18:23,541
[NAGASUMI THINKS]
How many times am I gonna

410
00:18:23,625 --> 00:18:25,875
have to be saved today?

411
00:18:28,541 --> 00:18:31,333
[SUN] If you just follow
this tunnel out you'll be fine.

412
00:18:31,750 --> 00:18:33,458
Come on, then!

413
00:18:33,541 --> 00:18:35,333
[VOICES]
Fishy tail!

414
00:18:35,416 --> 00:18:37,333
Leave this to me! 'kay.

415
00:18:37,416 --> 00:18:40,625
Um, well. I don't
need to run like you do.

416
00:18:40,708 --> 00:18:41,583
But doesn't it mean that

417
00:18:41,666 --> 00:18:43,541
