worry 'bout that.

419
00:18:45,791 --> 00:18:47,708
I am worried about it!

420
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:56,250
[NAGASUMI] Are you okay, Sun?

421
00:18:56,333 --> 00:18:58,333
I'm fine, are you okay?

422
00:18:58,416 --> 00:19:00,291
[NAGASUMI] Oh yeah,
I'm doing great.

423
00:19:00,375 --> 00:19:02,458
I wonder if Dad's
still chasing us.

424
00:19:02,541 --> 00:19:03,833
[SUN] You just called him "dad."

425
00:19:03,916 --> 00:19:05,750
[NAGASUMI] No, no!
That was a slip of the tongue!

426
00:19:05,833 --> 00:19:07,250
I meant to say your dad.

427
00:19:07,333 --> 00:19:09,000
[SUN] But Nagasumi,
if ya take me with ya,

428
00:19:09,083 --> 00:19:11,583
