435
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:30,166
Ya see, Nagasumi.

436
00:19:30,250 --> 00:19:32,541
If I saw somebody in
trouble right in front of me

437
00:19:32,625 --> 00:19:33,958
and I just ignored him,

438
00:19:34,041 --> 00:19:36,625
that would just disgrace
all Seto mermaids.

439
00:19:37,416 --> 00:19:42,291
'Cause honor among thieves...
is honor under the seas!

440
00:19:43,666 --> 00:19:46,375
[SUN] But I made this
decision on my own, ya see.

441
00:19:46,458 --> 00:19:49,000
And there's no reason for
it to get you in trouble.

442
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:51,250
It's fine...

443
00:19:51,333 --> 00:19:54,250
Don't you worry about me,
you just save yourself.

444
00:19:59,250 --> 00:20:01,416
[GOZABURO] There ya
are, ya little maggot!

445
00:20:04,250 --> 00:20:06,291
I knew I'd find ya.

446
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:10,666
Ya really think ya could
get away, you piss ant?

447
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:13,125
Take him down,
Octopus Nakajima!

448
00:20:13,208 --> 00:20:14,666
[OCTOPUS]
Oc-to-py!

449
00:20:14,750 --> 00:20:17,166
[NAGASUMI] He's huge!
But kind of cute.

450
00:20:17,250 --> 00:20:18,625
[OCTOPUS] Murdery!

451
00:20:18,708 --> 00:20:20,458
[SUN] Nagasumi!

452
00:20:22,291 --> 00:20:23,833
Nice shot, Octopus.

453
00:20:23,916 --> 00:20:25,375
Stop it, Dad!

454
00:20:25,458 --> 00:20:28,125
[GOZABURO] I can't really
say it's been nice knowin' ya.

455
00:20:28,750 --> 00:20:32,291
Not that I care, but ya
better say yer prayers.

456
00:20:35,750 --> 00:20:37,083
[NAGASUMI THINKS]
No matter what.

457
00:20:37,166 --> 00:20:39,250
I'll never be able to
run away from this lunatic.

458
00:20:39,625 --> 00:20:41,375
No Dad!
Stop it!

459
00:20:41,458 --> 00:20:43,250
Your death will save my

460
00:20:43,333 --> 00:20:46,958
