so take it like a man!

461
00:20:47,500 --> 00:20:48,666
[NAGASUMI]
Hold on!

462
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:51,500
I'd like permission to
marry your daughter sir!

463
00:20:51,958 --> 00:20:53,291
[REN] Well!

464
00:20:53,833 --> 00:20:55,041
[Sun gasps]

465
00:20:55,541 --> 00:20:57,500
[NAGASUMI THINKS] I have
to do this for Sun.

466
00:20:57,583 --> 00:21:00,625
I'll marry her, even
if it's just for show.

467
00:21:01,291 --> 00:21:04,250
And then she'll be free
to make up her own mind.

468
00:21:05,375 --> 00:21:08,791
Stop looking at me.
