469
00:21:10,541 --> 00:21:12,416
There you have it, Dad.

470
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:15,875
He said it.
Ya can't kill him.

471
00:21:16,916 --> 00:21:21,291
[GOZABURO] You maggot.
Think yer smart, huh?

472
00:21:21,375 --> 00:21:23,416
Think ya squirmed yer
way out this one, do you?

473
00:21:23,500 --> 00:21:25,500
Well you're wrong.

474
00:21:25,583 --> 00:21:28,458
[GOZABURO] I'll never
