00:21:30,791 --> 00:21:32,750
Really? You need to respect
your daughter's independence!

477
00:21:32,833 --> 00:21:34,208
Will you shut up?

478
00:21:34,291 --> 00:21:37,666
Any bastard that gets close to
Sun is gonna be fish food!

479
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:40,000
So I'm a dead man? Crap!

480
00:21:40,083 --> 00:21:41,791
C'mon, boss,
calm down now!

481
00:21:41,875 --> 00:21:43,375
[SUN] What do ya
think yer doing, Dad?

482
00:21:43,458 --> 00:21:44,750
[NAGASUMI THINKS]
I spent my summer vacation

483
00:21:44,833 --> 00:21:46,333
at the Seto Inland Sea.

484
00:21:46,416 --> 00:21:49,625
I went swimming. I hung
out with my Grandma.

485
00:21:49,708 --> 00:21:53,250
And then I wound up
taking a mermaid as my bride.

486
00:21:53,333 --> 00:21:54,833
[NAGASUMI]
Please let me go, Dad!

487
00:21:54,916 --> 00:21:57,208
[GOZABURO] How dare
you call me "dad"!

488
00:21:57,291 --> 00:21:58,375
[SUN] Stop it, Dad!

489
00:21:58,458 --> 00:21:59,708
[GOZABURO] Sink to
the bottom of the sea,

490
00:21:59,791 --> 00:22:01,416
ya fappy little shit!

491
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:02,625
[SUN] Nagasumi!

492
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:10,708
♪

493
00:23:34,791 --> 00:23:36,041
[NAGASUMI] Oh, man,
I can't believe I'm

494
00:23:36,125 --> 00:23:37,500
engaged to such a cute girl!

495
00:23:37,583 --> 00:23:40,041
And she's a mermaid!
A yakuza mermaid to boot!

496
00:23:40,125 --> 00:23:41,541
Geez, what should I do?

497
00:23:41,625 --> 00:23:43,708
What, I should take her on
a date to the summer festival?

498
00:23:43,791 --> 00:23:46,291
Alright then, I gotta stay
cool and keep it together.

499
00:23:46,375 --> 00:23:47,791
Can I do that?

